Style "FvwmTaskBar" NoTitle, Sticky, WindowListSkip, CirculateSkip

DestroyModuleConfig FvwmTaskBar*
*FvwmTaskBarGeometry +0+0

*FvwmTaskBarColorset 11
*FvwmTaskBarFocusColorset 12
*FvwmTaskBarIconColorset 13
*FvwmTaskBarTipsColorset 9

*FvwmTaskBarFont -adobe-helvetica-medium-r-*-*-12-*-*-*-*-*-*-*
*FvwmTaskBarSelFont -adobe-helvetica-bold-r-*-*-12-*-*-*-*-*-*-*
*FvwmTaskBarStatusFont fixed

*FvwmTaskBarAction Click1 FuncFvwmDeiconifyFocusAndRaise
*FvwmTaskBarAction Click2 Iconify
*FvwmTaskBarAction Click3 Popup MenuFvwmWindowOps2 Mouse c -102m

*FvwmTaskBarUseSkipList
*FvwmTaskBarUseIconNames
*FvwmTaskBarAutoStick
*FvwmTaskBarShowTips

*FvwmTaskBarButtonWidth 180
*FvwmTaskBarBellVolume 20
#*FvwmTaskBarMailBox /var/spool/mail/...
*FvwmTaskBarMailCommand FuncFvwmMail
*FvwmTaskBarClockFormat %H:%M

*FvwmTaskBarStartName Start
*FvwmTaskBarStartMenu MenuFvwmRoot Root +0p +32p
*FvwmTaskBarStartIcon 16x16/penguin.xpm

*FvwmTaskBarAutoHide

# Animation
